{"tid":880883,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"s8 lol 決賽 FNC vs IG ban pick 討論區","createTime":"2018-10-29T04:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T03:51:28.000Z","uid":87900,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"028574951150c1802f498b349b0853f999d4e917","tid":880883,"uid":87900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T04:33:13.000Z","msg":"預測FNC win<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48aa67db083df37f8e05ed35d8f6cc0fe42c1d8e","tid":880883,"uid":87900,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"IG<br />\n由於G2中上對線被打穿通關，所以對IG黎講無乜考驗。但之前比賽再加mic check得知，TheShy 係唔識聽中文，叫佢走佢就去開戰。所以TheShy團戰上好有可能會出事<br />\n<br />\n但佢地上中的確有資本做到線上壓制"},{"pid":"479f086ae3d04343041cdba0395b13f3af66b524","tid":880883,"uid":77880,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:30:05.000Z","msg":"幾時打"},{"pid":"4c582faf251abefbf764e39dfacf206ec5757fc2","tid":880883,"uid":87900,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T07:15:25.000Z","msg":"FNC<br />\n1. 打野波Sir依然on fire, 以表現計, IG應該要ban Leesin 以作尊重.<br />\n2. FNC中上對線實比IG差, 線上好大機會比人壓<br />\n3. 只要中上唔比人打爆, 去到團戰期even 經濟落後小小FNC 都可以穩住甚至打win團戰,<br />\n<br />\n所以我預期今次比賽會係IG中上先壓制, 之後利用優勢對下路/細龍入手, FNC會先守塔讓龍穩住局面, 之後透過營運/團戰波節奏反制局面. <br />\n<br />\n有幾點會好關鍵<br />\n1. FNC中上要盡量穩住對線, 唔可以比人打穿<br />\n2. 前期甚至開局波Sir好大可能會比人針對, 要好好保護波sir ge 開局<br />\n3. 可預期地IG會因為對線壓刀而有1-2K ge經濟優勢, 這波FNC真不虧, 但係FNC一定要保住個經濟, 呢點至關重要, FNC可以<br />\n- 守塔讓龍, 盡量清減少死亡同埋拖慢IG推塔速度<br />\n- 細龍可讓, 但峽谷先鋒要盡保住, 峽谷先鋒推塔太犀利<br />\n- 如塔真係保唔住, 應該要盡量交換資源<br />\n<br />\n總之穩定到個局勢FNC就可以利用本身長處係團戰期發力, <br />\n<br />\n反之IG就要針對返以上幾點, 儘量係開頭壓多D經濟, 儘量加快推塔節奏, 儘量snowball拉開經濟, 輾壓式咁WIN"},{"pid":"db346f4a97c5892ec0f518db63b8f5d7e22feead","tid":880883,"uid":87900,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T07:58:18.000Z","msg":"就ban pick上面, 後選方應該都會ban noc同akali <br />\n<br />\nIG<br />\n先選會ban viktor, Rakan, noc(唔知佢地點諗)<br />\n後選會ban viktor, noc, akali, 好大機會放leblanc<br />\n<br />\nFNC<br />\n先選應該會ban Jayce, Rakan, Aatrox. <br />\n後選應該會ban Jayce, Akali, Leblanc. <br />\n<br />\n咁樣ge話<br />\nIG先選可以會:<br />\nIG Aatrox<br />\nFNC Irelia/XinZhao<br />\nIG Lucian/Braum<br />\nFNC Alistar<br />\n<br />\nFNC先選可以會:<br />\nFNC Leblanc<br />\nIG Leesin/Ryze<br />\nFNC XinZhao/Braum<br />\nIG Alistar"},{"pid":"b64683c56fc1007908783254457c9e20294ae1e5","tid":880883,"uid":16178,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T08:09:54.000Z","msg":"s8 lol 決賽 FNC vs IG ban pick 一人討論區"},{"pid":"a85ac1dbc3fa0b14ee9db72b5e6607387212a6e3","tid":880883,"uid":10863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:55:52.000Z","msg":"希望有得睇the shy riven"},{"pid":"b2a1354eecb838c46d5f098066a6be0e10be21c2","tid":880883,"uid":24203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:58:41.000Z","msg":"FNC要保食屎狗<br />\n食屎狗 &gt; jkl"},{"pid":"e3fe454408b6890081290c58b95ff14a473f9b16","tid":880883,"uid":5970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:03:42.000Z","msg":"打返營運?"},{"pid":"365ecf677ac8e27312ce78e8cac652cc6d18e095","tid":880883,"uid":87900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3fe454408b6890081290c58b95ff14a473f9b16","tid":880883,"uid":5970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:03:42.000Z","msg":"打返營運?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:16:46.000Z","msg":"營運唔同左，係要頂得住前期ge營運，所以點都要有前期打架/線上能力"},{"pid":"53ddfc0a663f3e0c683d1ba30da1326873eae05b","tid":880883,"uid":87900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2a1354eecb838c46d5f098066a6be0e10be21c2","tid":880883,"uid":24203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:58:41.000Z","msg":"FNC要保食屎狗<br />\n食屎狗 &gt; jkl"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:18:03.000Z","msg":"Jkl 17